    "Kya mushkil waqt mein bhi ta'alluq Allah ke sath mazboot rehta hai?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "category": "Raat ki tanhaiyon mein Allah se judna aur Quran se dil jorna (Al-Muzzammil: 2-4)",
