    "Kya raat ke waqt dil naram ho kar Rab ke qareeb mehsoos hota hai?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "category": "Allah ka zikr mein rehna aur har woh cheez se katna jo Allah se door kare (Al-Muzzammil: 8)",
