    "Kya woh mehfilen /dost chhor diye gaye hain jo Allah se ghafil karte hain?",
    "Kya aise halqe apnaye gaye hain jahan Allah ki yaad barhti hai?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "category": "Mashriq-o-maghrib ke Rab ko pehchan'na aur us par tawakkal karna (Al-Muzzammil: 9)",
